  "body": "### What was wrong?\r\n\r\nIn the spec `eth_call` and `eth_estimateGas` take a `Transaction` content descriptor. This is not how clients work. The `Transaction` content descriptor has most (all?) fields `required`, and most should be optional instead.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
